channel.title: Compiler
channel.description:
I've been trying to fix my Compiler since forever. Every time I run my compiler it works perfectly. "Finished! Please Press anything to continue" Well when it does that and I go to my server to check out the update/change nothing changed stayed the same even if I compiled it right. Can anyone set up a new compiler or help me w. this one? I try to set up a new one but I don't know how too. I couldn't figure it out. Here's the code for the compiler I use now: (new one i tried to make) [code] @echo off title Stant Compiler javac *.java pause[/code]
The JAVA/JDK folders that show in my Computer > (C:) > Program Files > Java are: JKD1.6.0 , JDK1.6.0_21 , JRE1.6.0 , JRE1.6.0_03 , JRE6 . Those are all.
Sincerely, Imaginary.
